categories.name: Inci Talks
categories.page_desc:
We believe passionately in the power of ideas to change attitudes, lives of the student community. The goal of this event is to bring together the greatest achievers and eminent personalities such as yourself to plant the seed of an idea in the minds of this generation to create a positive change in the society. Jayaprakash Narayan (Loksatta Party Founder), Balaji Viswanathan (Highest followed person on Quora),Ricky Ken(Grammy award winning music composer),Dr Ullas Karanth(Renowned Environmentalist and Tiger expert),Ramaswami Balasubramaniam (Chairman of Grassroots Research And Advocacy Movement (GRAAM)) have adorned the stage of Inci-Talks in the previous editions.
